Type of Feat: General
Prerequisite: Str 13, one Stone Dragon maneuver.
Benefit: By Selecting this mode you take a penalty of -5 on your attack rolls.  You gain temporary hit points equal 10. These temporary hit points and your attack penalty last until the beginning of your next turn and are renewed each turn until this ability is deactivated.

This feat can be used in place of any feat that requires Power Attack as a prerequisite and that also does not directly modify the Power Attack feat itself (such as Improved Power Attack).

Use: Mode.